INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("3623","1","2016-06-14 12:47:41","2016-06-14 11:47:41","<div  class=\"one withsmallpadding ppb_header \" style=\"text-align:left;padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p>When building a truly unique and exquisite technical solution we at Communitec AV believe in using only the highest quality systems. These aesthetic and impressive systems are then discretely integrated and inter-connected into your home; allowing you full, and unprecedented, remote control.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3719 size-large\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2-1024x592.jpg\" alt=\"Integrated-Control2\" width=\"1024\" height=\"592\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Integrated Control</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">At Communitec, we recognise that simplicity is the key to any technical integration. It is for this reason that we offer multiple, intuitive and user-friendly control systems to choose from. These place all the functions of your remote controls and integrated technologies into one stylish handheld device. This device enables you to adjust and monitor your audio-visual media, lighting, shading, internal heating and household security from anywhere in your home.</span></p>\n<h5></h5>\n<p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Lightingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3850\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Lightingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Lightingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lighting, Shading and Electrical</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">The aesthetics achievable through innovative lighting solutions are not emphasised nearly as much as they should be. At Communitec we optimise all of our lighting solutions for comfort, as well as for the uniquely modern elegance made possible through the correct balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full and effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/IMG_1346-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3992\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/IMG_1346-1.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1346\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Heating and Cooling</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">We install intelligent heating and cooling systems, which learn your heating habits and daily schedule, from when you wish your house to be warmed to making adjustments when temperatures outside reach their peak. This innovative technical solution effortlessly optimises your comfort whilst saving energy.</span></p>\n<h5></h5>\n<p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/IMG_1346-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3992\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/IMG_1346-1.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1346\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Heating and Cooling</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">We install intelligent heating and cooling systems, which learn your heating habits and daily schedule, from when you wish your house to be warmed to making adjustments when temperatures outside reach their peak. This innovative technical solution effortlessly optimises your comfort whilst saving energy.</span></p>\n<h5></h5>\n<p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3845\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Networkingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Networking and Telecoms</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">After years of experience in Communitec IT, Communitec AV are experts in the installation and integration of fast and reliable high-speed broadband, structured cabling, and telephony systems: keeping you, your house and your contacts connected.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Home-Cinema.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3718 size-large\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Home-Cinema-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Home Cinema\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Home Cinema</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">Experience your favourite films, series or even television shows through the highest quality cinematic solutions. Whether it is to be the dramatic focus of a room or seamlessly integrated within it; Communitec AV can install the latest cinema systems, boasting high definition displays and 7.2 surround sound. These can be seamlessly fitted, and remote controlled via your mobile or tablet, allowing you to experience all the joys of a professional cinema but in the discrete, personal environment of your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3831\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\" alt=\"EXAMPLE OF COMMUNITEC AUDIO VISUAL WORK\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Security</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">As well as providing you and your house with high quality technology, we are also determined to help protect and defend your property from any kind of unwanted threat. Communitec AV provide a whole host of different security solutions including alarms, CCTV cameras, and smart locking systems so you can remotely control the security of your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3831\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\" alt=\"EXAMPLE OF COMMUNITEC AUDIO VISUAL WORK\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Security</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">As well as providing you and your house with high quality technology, we are also determined to help protect and defend your property from any kind of unwanted threat. Communitec AV provide a whole host of different security solutions including alarms, CCTV cameras, and smart locking systems so you can remotely control the security of your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3831\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\" alt=\"EXAMPLE OF COMMUNITEC AUDIO VISUAL WORK\" width=\"847