INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("3713","1","2016-06-15 18:36:50","2016-06-15 17:36:50","<div  class=\"one withsmallpadding ppb_header \" style=\"padding-bottom: 20px !important;text-align:center;padding:60px 0 60px 0;background-color:#ffffff;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><div class=\"ppb_subtitle\" style=\"\">Our audiovisual solutions are personalised for each space in which we work; they are designed, installed and integrated to bring to fruition the desire you have for any space or spaces in your household.</div><div class=\"page_header_sep center\"></div><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">When building a truly unique and exquisite technical solution to breathe new life into the interior design of any space, at Communitec, we believe in using only the highest quality systems. These aesthetic and impressive systems are then discretely integrated and inter-connected into your home; allowing you full, and unprecedented, remote control of your audiovisual media, lighting and shading, internal heating and your household&#8217;s security. Communitec&#8217;s AV solutions bring technology into design &#8211; becoming a seamless and impressive practical and aesthetic enhancement in the creation, or re-invention of any space.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><img src=\"http://themes.themegoods2.com/photome/demo/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/photo-1417436026361-a033044d901f-960x636.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Home Cinema</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">Experience your favourite films, series or even television shows through the highest quality cinematic solutions. Be the envy of your friends and family with a fully integrated cinema system, boasting high definition displays and 7.2 surround sound, which can be seamlessly fitted allowing you to experience all the joys of cinema in your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><img src=\"http://themes.themegoods2.com/photome/demo/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/post6-960x636.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Integrated Control</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">Communitec is proud to be able to offer multiple integrated control systems; this puts the functions of all of your remote controls into one stylish handheld device. This device enables you to adjust and monitor every installed feature, from your media systems, to your heating, lighting, air conditioning, even to the very security systems of your home.</span></p>\n<h5></h5>\n<p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><img src=\"http://themes.themegoods2.com/photome/demo/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/G77fvGNwSiE-960x636.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lighting and Shading</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">The aesthetics achievable through innovative lighting solutions are not emphasised nearly as much as they should be. At Communitec, we believe a uniquely modern elegance is achievable through the optimal balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full, effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div  class=\"one\" style=\"padding:0px 0 0px 0;\" ><div class=\"page_content_wrapper withbg\" style=\"background-image:url(http://themes.themegoods2.com/photome/demo/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/animals_horses_blondes_women_females_girls_models_mood_emotion_bokeh_babes_landscapes_trees_forests_winter_snow_moonlight_light_love_friends_photography_pose_plants_seasons.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;height:600px;position:relative;\"></div></div>\n<div  class=\"one ppb_fullwidth_button\" style=\"background-color:#222222;padding:30px 0 30px 0;\"><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><h2 class=\"title\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">What we can do for you.</h2><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border-color:#ffffff;color:#222222;\">Work with us</a></div></div>\n<div  class=\"one\" style=\"padding:0px 0 0px 0;\" ><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\" style=\"padding:0;\"><div class=\"one_half_bg\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://themes.themegoods2.com/photome/demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/post3.jpg\');height:600px;\"></div><div class=\"one_half_bg\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://themes.themegoods2.com/photome/demo/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/post2.jpg\');height:600px;\"></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_half withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">After years of experience in Communitec IT, Communitec are experts in the installation and integration of fast and reliable high-speed broadband, structured cabling, and telephony systems: keeping you,