INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("3921","2","2016-06-27 15:16:27","2016-06-27 14:16:27","<div  class=\"one withsmallpadding ppb_header \" style=\"padding-bottom: 20px !important;text-align:center;padding:20px 0 20px 0;background-color:#ffffff;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><div class=\"ppb_subtitle\" style=\"\">Our audiovisual solutions are personalised for each project in which we work; they are designed, installed and integrated to bring to fruition the desire you have for any space or spaces in your household.</div><div class=\"page_header_sep center\"></div><p>When building a truly unique and exquisite technical solution we at Communitec AV believe in using only the highest quality systems. These aesthetic and impressive systems are then discretely integrated and inter-connected into your home; allowing you full, and unprecedented, remote control.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Home-Cinema.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3718 size-large\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Home-Cinema-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Home Cinema\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Home Cinema</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">Experience your favourite films, series or even television shows through the highest quality cinematic solutions. Be the envy of your friends and family with a fully integrated cinema system, boasting high definition displays and 7.2 surround sound, which can be seamlessly fitted allowing you to experience all the joys of cinema in your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3719 size-large\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2-1024x592.jpg\" alt=\"Integrated-Control2\" width=\"1024\" height=\"592\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Integrated Control</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">Communitec is proud to be able to offer multiple integrated control systems; this puts the functions of all of your remote controls into one stylish handheld device. This device enables you to adjust and monitor every installed feature, from your media systems, to your heating, lighting, air conditioning, even to the very security systems of your home.</span></p>\n<h5></h5>\n<p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Lightingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3850\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Lightingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Lightingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lighting and Shading</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">The aesthetics achievable through innovative lighting solutions are not emphasised nearly as much as they should be. At Communitec, we believe a uniquely modern elegance is achievable through the optimal balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full, effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"divider one\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3831\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\" alt=\"EXAMPLE OF COMMUNITEC AUDIO VISUAL WORK\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Security</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">As well as providing you and your house with high quality technology we are also determined to help protect and defend your property from any kind of unwanted threat. Communitec provide a whole host of different security solutions including alarms, CCTV cameras, and smart locking systems so you can remotely control the security of your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3845\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Networkingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\