uniquely modern elegance is achievable through the optimal balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full, effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding: 30px 0 30px 0;\">\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"page_content_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"inner\">\r\n<div style=\"margin: auto; width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Lightingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3850\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Lightingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Lightingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lighting and Shading</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">The aesthetics achievable through innovative lighting solutions are not emphasised nearly as much as they should be. At Communitec, we believe a uniquely modern elegance is achievable through the optimal balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full, effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding: 30px 0 30px 0;\">\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"page_content_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"inner\">\r\n<div style=\"margin: auto; width: 100%;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co