\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">The aesthetics achievable through innovative lighting solutions are not emphasised nearly as much as they should be. At Communitec we optimise all of our lighting solutions for comfort, as well as for the uniquely modern elegance made possible through the correct balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full and effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"divider one\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3831\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Security-2.jpg\" alt=\"EXAMPLE OF COMMUNITEC AUDIO VISUAL WORK\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Security</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">As well as providing you and your house with high quality technology we are also determined to help protect and defend your property from any kind of unwanted threat. Communitec provide a whole host of different security solutions including alarms, CCTV cameras, and smart locking systems so you can remotely control the security of your home.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3845\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Networkingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Networking and Telecoms</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">After years of experience in Communitec IT, Communitec are experts in the installation and integration of fast and reliable high-speed broadband, structured cabling, and telephony systems: keeping you, your house and your contacts connected.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3719\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2.jpg\" alt=\"Integrated-Control2\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1183\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">HVAC</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">We install intelligent heating and cooling systems, which learn your heating habits and daily schedule, from when you wish your house to be warmed to making adjustments when temperatures outside reach their peak. This innovative technical solution effortlessly optimises your comfort whilst saving energy.</span></p>\n<h5></h5>\n<p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div  class=\"one\" style=\"padding:0px 0 0px 0;\" ><div class=\"page_content_wrapper withbg\" style=\"background-image:url(http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Services.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;height:600px;position:relative;\"></div></div>\n<div  class=\"one ppb_fullwidth_button\" style=\"background-color:#222222;padding:30px 0 30px 0;\"><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><h2 class=\"title\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">What we can do for you.</h2><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border-color:#ffffff;color:#222222;\">Work with us</a></div></div>\n","Services","","inherit","closed","closed","","3623-revision-v1","","","2016-06-27 15:32:45","2016-06-27 14:32:45","","3623","http://171991.communitec.co/3623-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0");
