its and daily schedule, from when you wish your house to be warmed to making adjustments when temperatures outside reach their peak. This innovative technical solution effortlessly optimises your comfort whilst saving energy.</span>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding: 30px 0 30px 0;\">\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"page_content_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"inner\">\r\n<div style=\"margin: auto; width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3719\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Integrated-Control2.jpg\" alt=\"Integrated-Control2\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1183\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">HVAC</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">We install intelligent heating and cooling systems, which learn your heating habits and daily schedule, from when you wish your house to be warmed to making adjustments when temperatures outside reach their peak. This innovative technical solution effortlessly optimises your comfort whilst saving energy.</span>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding: 30px 0 30px 0;\">\r\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"page_content_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"inner\">\r\n<div style=\"margin: auto; width: 100%;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3845\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Networkingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: ce