unitec we optimise all of our lighting solutions for comfort, as well as for the uniquely modern elegance made possible through the correct balancing of natural and artificial light. Through the carefully considered installation of subtle lighting solutions and remotely controlled custom curtains and blinds, our AV systems allow you full and effortless control over the look and feel of any space in which they are installed.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"divider one\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third last withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3845\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Networkingresized.jpg\" alt=\"Networkingresized\" width=\"847\" height=\"489\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Networking and Telecoms</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: #000000;\">After years of experience in Communitec IT, Communitec AV are experts in the installation and integration of fast and reliable high-speed broadband, structured cabling, and telephony systems: keeping you, your house and your contacts connected.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div  class=\"one_third withsmallpadding ppb_text\" style=\"padding:30px 0 30px 0;\" ><div class=\"standard_wrapper\"><div class=\"page_content_wrapper\"><div class=\"inner\"><div style=\"margin:auto;width:100%\"><p><a href=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Home-Cinema.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3718 size-large\" src=\"http://171991.communitec.co/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Home-Cinema-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Home Cinema\" width=